usage: git hooks [-r] -- <module-paths>

Install/update git hooks provided by zou.

    -h|--help               display help
    -r|--recursive          visit specified modules recursively
    -a|--all                visit all submodules (skip SKU filter)
    -x|--external           visit external submodules (skip external filter)
    -f|--force              force update
    +                       equivalent to --recursive --all --external --force
    <module-paths>          specific modules to visit (default to current module)
    
example:
    git hooks -r            install git hooks recursively
